Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:10.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something that's very important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.71,0:01:14.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I might not even remember my own face soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:15.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.21,0:01:16.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.54,0:01:17.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:19.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagiri Pharmaceuticals, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:22.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really where those human experiments are being conducted?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.96,0:01:24.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not Harima Mika...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.60,0:01:28.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can use as much money however you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.39,0:01:30.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.43,0:01:32.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Celty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.84,0:02:11.47,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them are fakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:14.10,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is filled with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:18.95,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,They say things like, "I love you," and, "I like you," just to tie others down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:21.48,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,"Look this way," and, "Stay by my side."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:24.24,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,They just covet and fawn on people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:27.29,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,My love is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.71,0:02:34.71,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a broader, more complete thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.71,0:02:44.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.73,0:02:47.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the money transfer. See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:52.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to get you something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:57.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See, from that vending machine right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:03.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:32.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:36.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:43.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They still haven't been found?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:46.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm incredibly sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:49.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world was security doing, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:51.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the person in charge,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:57.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,they were staying in the same hotel, but Seiji suddenly \Nchanged locations in the middle of the night—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:04:01.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I could still reach him on his cell phone at seven PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:03.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If something were to happen to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:10.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He promised he wouldn't leave Ikebukuro,\N so I believe we'll find him soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:11.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:16.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think will happen to us if the police get wind of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:18.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:21.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:23.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:24.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Director...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:26.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:33.87,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, it was just a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:40.06,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Like one of the expensive, beautiful dolls my \Nuncle would buy for me on his trips overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:45.00,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't like dolls when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:53.68,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume he wasn't trying to please me,\N but just kept sending me things he liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.14,0:05:01.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Seiji, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:03.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:14.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you think this one over here is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:14.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:19.54,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It was always utterly silent in that house, and we were always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:24.76,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Even before my younger brother was born,\N my uncle often had to look after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.76,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I could also enter and leave his study whenever I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:34.60,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...where it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:42.69,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,My uncle would sometimes gaze at that thing he'd\N smuggled in from overseas as if he were in a trance...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:45.86,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes he'd even talk to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:48.99,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly was beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:51.56,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,More so than any doll he'd ever given me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:59.31,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't seem mysterious or cruel; it seemed\N like just its head was a whole creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:02.54,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's all it was to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:09.18,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, when I secretly invited my brother into the study...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.69,0:06:12.18,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we'd just have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:15.68,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I may have simply wanted to share my secret with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:18.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:34.33,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the beginning of it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:39.21,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,940)}My one and only regret, which continues to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:53.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time we've met, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:58.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did that list of illegal immigrants\N prove useful to you, Ms. Yagiri Namie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:01.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:06.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To have the director of the sixth research\N facility come all the way to a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:10.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, sit anywhere over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:16.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency. Find out where my brother is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.88,0:07:21.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you however much you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:24.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been able to contact him since last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:26.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He should be somewhere in Ikebukuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:28.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that much time has passed, has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:30.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:34.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's with a girl; one who has a wound on her neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:36.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:39.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's at that age, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:42.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:47.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't there many more important things we should investigate first?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:53.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are rumors going around that your company is \Nabout to be taken over by that foreign company Nebula, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:55.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's true, then your position—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:59.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Orihara Izaya, I don't have time for idle chitchat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:01.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:05.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That such a capable woman as yourself \Nwould be in love with her younger brother, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:07.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:11.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Yagiri Namie I know is quite a distinguished woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:14.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, even though it was a family business,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:20.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,your father screwed up and had to hand it over\N to your uncle, who doesn't do you any favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:26.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you had to use your own abilities to get the job,\Nand now you've come this far, despite being so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:28.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're also very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:32.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly do know me well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:35.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be easy for you to search for my brother, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:38.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your brother, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:40.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't interfere with his business, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:43.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interfering!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:45.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one who can protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:50.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems stalkers never do realize what they're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:52.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They always say they're protecting their—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:55.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't group me together with any stalkers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:57.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:58.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:00.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:03.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we'll do things my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:05.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Information dealers are different from the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:16.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What rules do you play by...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:18.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:22.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you jealous of that girl with the wound on her neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:24.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:31.99,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'd be jealous of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.99,0:09:36.56,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,A chest-burning jealousy that dyes people a rusty red...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:40.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...I have...someone I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:46.55,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew Seiji was slowly getting stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:53.18,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd go into our uncle's study for no reason at all, then stare at that thing every time he snuck in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:55.72,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiji wasn't in love with a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:59.20,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It had no soul, or even a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:11.15,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to take Seiji's mind off of it, so I asked my uncle\N if I could move it as soon as I entered the company, 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:14.52,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,and brought it to the facility as a research subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:19.92,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.92,0:10:22.29,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Nebula began contacting us,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.29,0:10:28.06,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1017)}and just when I started losing my mind, trying not to\N let any information leak, my security card was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.97,0:10:31.41,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The card that only I had...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:44.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, I might have killed someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:46.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:53.25,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And what welled-up in my chest at that moment was neither fear nor anger, but unbounded joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:56.76,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiji needed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:13.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:16.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave everything to your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:17.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:21.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, about her—not that girl over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:24.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you did take her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:26.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:29.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave everything about her to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:32.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:42.51,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, I didn't realize there was a \Nstupid girl named Harima Mika stalking Seiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:46.97,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1400)}After she invaded his room without permission and saw "it," Seiji just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:51.97,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:53.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:57.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, you don't have to panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:12:00.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The police should be picking them up and contacting you shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I did say "police," but you should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:07.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:08.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:10.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't toy with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:15.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.86,0:12:17.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:42.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:45.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:47.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, we still...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:49.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:57.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy you love me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:13:00.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:03.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:05.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:08.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, take me far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:14.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be alone with you, too, but where would we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:17.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:19.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A lovers' quarrel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:19.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:42.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:44.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.36,0:13:47.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:50.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not bad people or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:52.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:52.68,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,Just listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:55.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let...me...go! Let...me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:04.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:07.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:14.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alright. It doesn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:15.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:19.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it, but you have to chase her, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.28,0:14:22.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to say this:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:26.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to me and go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:29.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:53.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, so-sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:55.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:58.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:04.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:08.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:14.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, "Let me go!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:17.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:19.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she's my destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:22.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does she look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:23.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'd know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:28.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaaaat's thaaaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:42.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you don't know your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:44.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a bit irresponsible?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:45.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:49.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff like that's not important when you love someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:51.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:52.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:54.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's she your destiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:56.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I love her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:57.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:16:01.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't use another word for it besides "love!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:05.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:14.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The black bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:16.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm going to act on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:17.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:18.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:23.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you a lot more than Izaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:26.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll leave it at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:39.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to bleed if I pull this out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:41.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pull it out after I buy some band-aids.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.32,0:16:44.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, maybe an instant adhesive would be better?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.39,0:16:57.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, your head was walking around attached to another body...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:17:00.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When you caught it, a high schooler interfered...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:03.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then another high schooler appeared when you were chasing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:05.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And he ran off with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:08.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to believe all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:11.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ask you to believe it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:13.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:15.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But why was Shizuo there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:18.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd completely forgotten about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:24.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting in the park while on a job from Izaya, \Nwhen Shizuo happened to pass by, so we started talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:31.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I got a message afterward saying the job was canceled, so it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:35.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Orihara, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:38.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I wanted to talk to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:40.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're still confused, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:43.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll listen to whatever you have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:50.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is my head on someone else's body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:57.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the dark, seeing as I didn't witness \Nthe events, but if I could venture a guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.04,0:17:58.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What if...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:05.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It found a girl who looked like she had your build and attached itself to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:07.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's horrifying...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.93,0:18:10.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It could've found a newly dead corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.04,0:18:13.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:17.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...no...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:19.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:24.98,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,What I did wasn't wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:29.79,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,870)}Creating that girl with the body from that incident...For Seiji's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:31.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:33.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:35.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:35.25,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:37.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was scary, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:37.28,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But nothing went wrong, did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:46.44,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,My love never faltered, even when she ran away and met up with Seiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:49.73,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiji's love uses my love for him as a stepping-stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:54.90,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He knows that, and I know that he knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:58.07,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's twisted, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:01.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, that was a Raira Academy uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:03.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:07.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, so just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:10.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we've got to find a girl from Raira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.39,0:19:12.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then all I can do is meet my head and talk with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.70,0:19:16.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the head that could only scream when it saw you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:22.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you going to do about a head that's living as a complete person?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:26.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me you'd separate it from its body for your own sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:32.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Celty...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:34.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to admit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.26,0:19:38.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That I've lost my head and my memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.75,0:19:43.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That all my efforts these past twenty years have been in vain...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:47.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't been in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:51.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get her back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:53.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:20:00.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, where's your cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:00.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you lose it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:03.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:06.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't there, even though I put it in my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:07.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:10.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She...needs me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:13.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.53,0:20:16.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:20.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright. Leave everything to your big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:26.48,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,What nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.65,0:20:33.51,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Dolls should act like dolls and do as they're told.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.51,0:20:36.50,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And not interfere with my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:38.46,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:40.52,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to regret anything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.52,0:20:42.47,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.39,0:20:44.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.53,0:20:49.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Circulate a message to all our underlings.\N I don't care whether she dies or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:53.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on the circumstances, dispose of her on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.01,0:21:20.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:21.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:23.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:24.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:26.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:32.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so, so, so many things even I don't know in this town that continually appear and disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:35.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I can't leave a city where so many people gather!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:37.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People love!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.43,0:21:38.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I like people!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.76,0:21:40.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:40.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.29,0:21:48.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People should love me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.39,0:21:56.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.68,0:21:58.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel any calmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.47,0:22:00.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you answer questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.66,0:22:05.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you didn't remember anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,0:22:10.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, that means...umm...you have amnesia?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.76,0:22:17.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it again, but I think you should go to the police or a hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.26,0:22:19.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:26.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.51,0:22:25.50,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.50,0:22:26.78,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.55,0:22:29.32,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.32,0:22:32.03,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Before she interferes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:35.24,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever and ever—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.24,0:22:36.70,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.61,0:22:39.00,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.87,0:22:41.50,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.51,0:22:44.25,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.18,0:24:16.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.43,0:24:20.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The headless rider, Orihara Izaya, and the \Ngirl with the wounded neck appeared again...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.89,0:24:23.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And to top it all off, a guy from the next class over is in The Dollars!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.18,0:24:25.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time: The First and Only.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.14,0:24:29.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a dream where I was leading an abnormal life, yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.03,0:24:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
